## 6. CSS (`public/style.css`)

Add styles for option buttons and selected state:
```css
.message-options { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px; }
.msg-option-btn {
  font-size: 10px;
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 3px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  background: none;
  color: var(--text);
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: inherit;
  transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
}
.msg-option-btn:hover:not(:disabled) { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
.msg-option-btn.selected { background: var(--accent); color: var(--bg); border-color: var(--accent); }
.msg-option-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: default; }
```

**Remove** `.approval-reply-input` styles.

